description:
During this introductory course on using Microsoft Excel 2010, we'll teach the basics of using Microsoft Excel 2010.

Your professional instructor will talk you through Excel 2010's features, starting with the basics, from creating files to editing existing documents. You'll start with creating a new workbook and entering text and numbers, moving onto saving and printing your documents.


The course is designed for individuals and office professionals who need to learn the basics of Microsoft Excel 2010.
title: Introduction to Microsoft Excel 2010
